page.title: 19FENSTANTON PEOPLE
page.content: There are lots of interesting people in Fenstanton,we have interviewed a few.Here are {Mr.Dunn}and {Mr.Hobbs.} { * Mr.Julian Dunn * {is a full_time radio disc Jockey}.He works for{Radio Cambridgeshire.}His other favourite radio station is Radio 1.His favourite sports are football and speedway.He has interviewed many famous people.He lives at Little Moor, Fenstanton { * Mr.Tony Hobbs * is{Fenstanton Village Postmaster.}He gets between{500_600}letters a day, {5_10}parcels and{40_50}packages.His hobby is keeping bees.He looks after {Fenstanton Village Clock Tower.}He is superstitious.He likes working in the post_office and has been there for 30 years.{He lives at the Village {Post_Office,High Street, Fenstanton.
